9EF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub66.ezboard.com/umukhtaribnasim.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mukhtar Ibn Asim</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 85<br> <font color=#B76D00>(7/21/01 10:44:21 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Member of the Coalition</span><hr size=1> 1. Talk with some of the LCG council members. (Nephyur, Eshtara, Stasia, and myself come to mind).<br><br>2. Try and have your members group with members of LCG guilds.<br><br>3. Try and come to a few LCG events... we aren't going to exclude anyone if we can help it.  Even people outside LCG.<br><br>4. Once you've done 1-3 for a couple weeks, re-contact the council member you spoke with and let them know if you still want in.  At that point we will discuss it on the council forum and either vote to admit your guild, or inform you of any concerns we have that we want addressed before admitting your guild.<br><br><br>Good luck!<br><br> <p>****************<BR>Mukhtar Ibn Asim<BR>****************<BR>Gatekeeper, Wander of Norrath,<BR>and Guardian of Dawn</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5DBE6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub66.ezboard.com/unephyur.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nephyur</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Gatekeeper</span><br>  Posts: 111<br> <font color=#B76D00>(7/22/01 11:29:27 pm)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.techniartist.com/9realms/captions/neph.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Member of the Coalition</span><hr size=1> /nod<br><br>I've tried numerous times to access your web page, but bee